#: ../../07-removed.rst:3
msgid "删除的功能"
msgstr "Removed Features"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:7
msgid "删除 ``paddle`` 模式的支持"
msgstr "Removed support for ``paddle`` mode"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:9
msgid ""
"``paddlepaddle-tiny`` 已停更， 仅支持 Python ≤3.6 现代 Python（3.8+）必须装完整 "
"``paddle`` ，体积大、安装易报错"
msgstr "``paddlepaddle-tiny`` has been discontinued and only supports Python ≤3.6. Modern Python (3.8+) requires the full ``paddle`` package, which is large and prone to installation errors."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:12
msgid "精度：不如现代 PaddleNLP、LLM 分词、BERT/ERNIE 小模型"
msgstr "Accuracy: Not as good as modern PaddleNLP, LLM segmentation, or small BERT/ERNIE models."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:13
msgid "速度：远慢于默认模式"
msgstr "Speed: Much slower than the default mode."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:14
msgid "社区：极少项目生产环境用 paddle 模式"
msgstr "Community: Very few projects use the paddle mode in production environments."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:16
msgid ""
"LAC (Lexical Analysis of Chinese) 是百度开源的中文词法分析工具， 基于深度学习框架 "
"``PaddlePaddle`` 实现。"
msgstr "LAC (Lexical Analysis of Chinese) is an open-source Chinese lexical analysis tool from Baidu, implemented based on the ``PaddlePaddle`` deep learning framework."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:18
msgid "``lac_small`` 在 ``jieba`` 中的用途"
msgstr "Usage of ``lac_small`` in ``jieba``"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:20
msgid "``lac_small`` 是 ``jieba`` 的 ``paddle`` 模式的核心组件， 用于提供基于深度学习的分词和词性标注功能。"
msgstr "``lac_small`` is the core component of the ``paddle`` mode in ``jieba``, used to provide deep learning-based segmentation and part-of-speech tagging functions."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:24
msgid "生成的文件的维护"
msgstr "Maintenance of Generated Files"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:26
msgid "原代码库为什么会有 ``.p`` 和 ``.py`` 两种文件？ 这是为了兼容性和性能做的权衡："
msgstr "Why are there both ``.p`` and ``.py`` files in the original codebase? This is a trade-off for compatibility and performance:"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:28
msgid ""
"``.p`` 文件 (Pickle)：这是 Python 的二进制序列化格式. 用途：主要用于 Jython（运行在 Java 虚拟机上的 "
"Python）。"
msgstr "``.p`` files (Pickle): This is Python's binary serialization format. Usage: Primarily for Jython (Python running on the Java Virtual Machine)."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:29
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``.py`` 文件 (Python 源码)：这些文件里通常只有一行： ``P = {...}`` ，把数据存成了一个巨大的字典常量。 "
"用途：用于标准的 CPython。 Python 解释器对加载编译好的 ``.pyc`` 字节码优化得很好， 直接导入模块比解析 Pickle "
"文件在某些环境下更安全、启动更快， 且不容易出现版本兼容问题。"
msgstr "``.py`` files (Python source): These files usually contain only one line: ``P = {...}``, storing the data as a huge dictionary constant. Usage: For standard CPython. The Python interpreter optimizes the loading of compiled ``.pyc`` bytecode very well. Directly importing the module is safer and faster than parsing a Pickle file in some environments, and it is less prone to version compatibility issues."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:33
msgid "两个文件夹之间的重复（finalseg vs posseg）"
msgstr "Repetition between Two Folders (finalseg vs posseg)"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:35
msgid "``finalseg`` 和 ``posseg`` 里都有 ``prob_start.py`` 等文件，这是因为："
msgstr "Both ``finalseg`` and ``posseg`` contain files like ``prob_start.py`` because:"

#: ../../07-removed.rst:37
msgid "``finalseg`` ：负责分词（判断一个字是 B/M/E/S）。"
msgstr "``finalseg``: Responsible for segmentation (determining if a character is B/M/E/S)."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:38
msgid "``posseg`` ：负责词性标注（判断一个词是 n/v/adj 等）。"
msgstr "``posseg``: Responsible for part-of-speech tagging (determining if a word is n/v/adj, etc.)."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:40
msgid ""
"它们底层都使用了 HMM（隐马尔可夫模型）， 所以都需要“初始概率 (start)”、“转移概率 (trans)”和“发射概率 (emit)”。 "
"注意：虽然文件名一样，但里面的数据是不一样的！ ``posseg`` 的状态空间（States）比 ``finalseg`` 复杂得多， "
"所以它们的概率矩阵维度不同，不能混用。"
msgstr "Both use HMM (Hidden Markov Model) at the base, so they both require \"initial probability (start)\", \"transition probability (trans)\", and \"emission probability (emit)\". Note: Although the filenames are the same, the data inside is different! The state space (States) of ``posseg`` is much more complex than that of ``finalseg``, so their probability matrix dimensions are different and cannot be mixed."

#: ../../07-removed.rst:44
msgid ""
"重构这个项目，进行以下改进： 项目明确不支持 Jython（现在的 Python 项目很少支持 Jython 了）， 可以删除所有的 ``.p``"
" 文件。 简化 ``__init__.py`` 中的加载逻辑， 只保留 ``from .prob_start import P`` 。 "
"这样能显著减少包的大小 and 复杂度。"
msgstr "Refactoring this project to make the following improvements: The project explicitly does not support Jython (few modern Python projects support Jython), so all ``.p`` files can be deleted. Simplify the loading logic in ``__init__.py``, keeping only ``from .prob_start import P``. This can significantly reduce the package size and complexity."
